{
  "id": "5ea64b32de34c90017a17b2b",
  "title": "署名と捺印に関する法律まとめ",
  "created": 1587956597,
  "updated": 1592900042,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ea64b32de34c90017a17b2b",
      "text": "署名と捺印に関する法律まとめ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956597,
      "updated": 1587965091
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64b9aaff09e0000b586a6",
      "text": "商法中署名スヘキ場合ニ關スル法律 1900年",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956634,
      "updated": 1587958859
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64b9aaff09e0000b586a9",
      "text": " 明治33年2月26日法律第17号",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956634,
      "updated": 1587970947
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64b9aaff09e0000b586aa",
      "text": " 施行: 明治33年3月18日 → 法例第1条",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956634,
      "updated": 1587970947
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64b9aaff09e0000b586ab",
      "text": " 廃止: 平成18年5月1日 → 会社法の施行に伴う関係法律の整備等に関する法律第1条第1号",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956634,
      "updated": 1587970947
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64b74aff09e0000b586a2",
      "text": ">法律第十七號",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956597,
      "updated": 1587956600
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64b75aff09e0000b586a4",
      "text": ">商法中署名スヘキ場合ニ於テハ記名捺印ヲ以テ署名ニ代フルコトヲ得",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956597,
      "updated": 1587956602
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64b7aaff09e0000b586a5",
      "text": "https://ja.wikisource.org/wiki/商法中署名スヘキ場合ニ關スル法律",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956602,
      "updated": 1587956660
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64bb4aff09e0000b586af",
      "text": "　[署名]の代わりに[記名捺印]でも良い、とした法律",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956661,
      "updated": 1592899949
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea655beaff09e0000f1bf1d",
      "text": "　1900年当時、自分の名前を書くことができない人が2割程度いた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587959230,
      "updated": 1587959267
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea6557aaff09e0000f1bf1c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587959162,
      "updated": 1587959162
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64bb4aff09e0000b586b0",
      "text": "会社法の施行に伴う関係法律の整備等に関する法律 2005年",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956661,
      "updated": 1587958906
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65755aff09e0000e32306",
      "text": "[会社法の施行に伴う関係法律の整備等に関する法律 http://www.shugiin.go.jp/internet/itdb_housei.nsf/html/housei/16220050726087.htm]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587959637,
      "updated": 1587959732
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64c6caff09e0000b586b3",
      "text": ">第一条　次に掲げる法律は、廃止する。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956844,
      "updated": 1587960586
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65b09aff09e0000e3231f",
      "text": "> 　一　商法中署名すべき場合に関する法律（明治三十三年法律第十七号）...",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587960586,
      "updated": 1587960592
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65b08aff09e0000e3231c",
      "text": ">... ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587960585,
      "updated": 1587960598
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65b09aff09e0000e3231d",
      "text": "> 第六十四条　商法の一部を次のように改正する。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587960585,
      "updated": 1587960585
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65818aff09e0000e3230c",
      "text": "> ...第一編を次のように改める。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587959832,
      "updated": 1587959835
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea6581eaff09e0000e3230f",
      "text": "> ...第八章　雑則",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587959838,
      "updated": 1587959863
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65836aff09e0000e32310",
      "text": "> 　第三十二条　この法律の規定により署名すべき場合には、記名押印をもって、署名に代えることができる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587959863,
      "updated": 1587959866
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65836aff09e0000e32313",
      "text": "> 　第三十三条から第五百条まで　削除",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587959871,
      "updated": 1587959871
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea6575eaff09e0000e32309",
      "text": "　商法32条に組み込まれた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587959871,
      "updated": 1587961759
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65f91aff09e0000f1bf1f",
      "text": "\t\t[記名押印]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587961745,
      "updated": 1592899987
    },
    {
      "id": "5ef1b994aff09e000004f0a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1592899988,
      "updated": 1592899988
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65af3aff09e0000e32316",
      "text": " 会社法",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587960564,
      "updated": 1587960565
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65af4aff09e0000e32318",
      "text": " 　署名と記名押印が併記されている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587960565,
      "updated": 1587960565
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65af4aff09e0000e32319",
      "text": " \t>[* 署名し、又は記名押印]しなければならない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587960565,
      "updated": 1587960565
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65af4aff09e0000e3231a",
      "text": " \t>電磁的記録をもって作成されている場合における当該電磁的記録に記録された事項については、法務省令で定める[* 署名又は記名押印]に代わる措置をとらなければならない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587960565,
      "updated": 1587960565
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65af3aff09e0000e32317",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587960564,
      "updated": 1587960564
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65b47aff09e0000e32324",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587960648,
      "updated": 1587960648
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65b33aff09e0000e32323",
      "text": "商法及び国際海上物品運送法の一部を改正する法律",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587960627,
      "updated": 1587960627
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64cb3aff09e0000b586b6",
      "text": "商法第32条を削除",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587956915,
      "updated": 1587960641
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea653eaaff09e0000b586d2",
      "text": "\t[法務省：商法及び国際海上物品運送法の一部を改正する法律について http://www.moj.go.jp/MINJI/minji07_00219.html]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587958762,
      "updated": 1587958971
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea654bfaff09e0000b586d4",
      "text": "\t平成３１年４月１日から施行",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587958975,
      "updated": 1587958976
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64ff4aff09e0000b586d0",
      "text": "\thttp://www.moj.go.jp/content/001261326.pdf",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957748,
      "updated": 1587958973
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64feeaff09e0000b586ce",
      "text": "なぜなのだろう？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957742,
      "updated": 1587961786
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65fb9aff09e0000f1bf20",
      "text": "　>削除されたのは、32条にまとめずに、署名が規定されている各条文を「署名し、又は記名押印し」のように、各条文の事情に適した規定に個別化したためです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587961786,
      "updated": 1588048750
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea7b373aff09e00007a62a2",
      "text": "　 https://www.facebook.com/1129148772/posts/10221505944334532?d=n&sfns=mo",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1588048755,
      "updated": 1588048789
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65860aff09e0000e32314",
      "text": "---",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587959905,
      "updated": 1587959907
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea65860aff09e0000e32315",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587959905,
      "updated": 1587959905
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64dc7aff09e0000b586ba",
      "text": "民事訴訟法",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957192,
      "updated": 1587957438
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64e38aff09e0000b586be",
      "text": ">（文書の成立）",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957304,
      "updated": 1587957441
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64eb1aff09e0000b586c5",
      "text": ">第二百二十八条　文書は、その成立が真正であることを証明しなければならない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957426,
      "updated": 1587957444
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64eb1aff09e0000b586c6",
      "text": ">...４　私文書は、本人又はその代理人の[* 署名又は押印]があるときは、[真正に成立]したものと推定する。...",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957426,
      "updated": 1592900042
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64eb1aff09e0000b586c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957456,
      "updated": 1592900038
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64ee9aff09e0000b586ca",
      "text": "電子署名及び認証業務に関する法律",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957481,
      "updated": 1587958836
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64dc7aff09e0000b586bb",
      "text": "https://www8.cao.go.jp/kisei-kaikaku/suishin/meeting/bukai/20171120/171120bukai01.pdf",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957192,
      "updated": 1587957192
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64dc8aff09e0000b586bd",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/b48bfc059aca944e16fd28e5097d9892]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957192,
      "updated": 1587957689
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64fb9aff09e0000b586cc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957689,
      "updated": 1587957689
    },
    {
      "id": "5ea64f43aff09e0000b586cb",
      "text": "[二段の推定]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1587957572,
      "updated": 1588048979
    }
  ]
}